      "rationale": "The continuum linear-elastic model with frictional contact (mu=0.2) at the screw-rod and rod-tulip interfaces is consistent with prior FDA-published validation studies for ASTM F1717 constructs. The model form is appropriate for predicting global construct stiffness and yield-region behavior within the tested load range."
