      "rationale": "Eleven production-equivalent non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were procured with full lot traceability. Pre-test dimensional inspection confirmed all constructs within drawing tolerances. Sample size is consistent with ASTM F1717 requirements and provides adequate statistical power for the comparison metric used."
