      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 loading configuration (5-degree lordotic angle, standard block geometry). While the protocol is well-controlled and reproducible across two laboratories, only one test condition was evaluated. This limits the ability to characterize model sensitivity to test condition variation and represents the one factor below the required credibility level."
