      "rationale": "A parameter mapping table was prepared documenting the correspondence between each FEA input (geometry, material, boundary condition, loading rate) and the measured or specified test condition. Discrepancies were quantified and propagated through uncertainty analysis. No unresolved parameter mismatches were identified."
