      "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfied both acceptance criteria. Stiffness: 4.8% difference, E/uval=0.87. Yield force: 7.3% difference, E/uval=1.42. Force at 40 mm: 6.1% difference, E/uval=1.21. Results are consistent across both test laboratories, confirming model predictive capability."
