      "rationale": "The three selected QoIs — construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement — are the primary performance metrics specified in ASTM F1717 and directly inform the regulatory decision regarding mechanical equivalence of the non-cannulated design. The QoIs are clinically relevant as they characterize both elastic behavior and post-yield performance under physiological-representative loading."
